sentences: Hardin was born in 1945 in Tulsa, Oklahoma.
Her rise to country music popularity began in 1983 with her first single for RCA Records single, the top 10 hit "After The Last Goodbye."
On February 17, 1996, Hardin died in a car accident on Highway 20 west of Salina, Oklahoma near her home in the Lake Hudson area.
